data.description: DO NOT MISS THIS AMAZING PROPERTY.  Come see this diamond in the rough and make an offer!  Just think about it...no more boarding your horse!!  This nearly flat and fully fenced 2.9 acres is a beautiful property that has a loafing shed with 2+ stalls and great spaces for a tack room, hay storage, large shop and more.  The turn around drive makes for easy access to RV parking, horses and livestock.  The large field area can be made into proper pastures or a space that works for you.  The wood stove in the shop is negotiable.  This property has an original mid 60's style single level ranch with lots of new updates.  New paint throughout the entire house in the past month.  Main bathroom completely remodeled in the past month to include dual sinks and new updated finishes. Original hardwoods throughout.  New roof in 2023.  Has a septic tank but on public water.  There is a playground area, fruit trees, fire pit, a beautiful back patio with a perfect western view of the sunset, and a beautiful water feature near the front stone patio.  Fresh exterior paint within the past 3 years.  This house has great bones, move in ready, will have a new stove top put in before closing, and with a little TLC can really shine.  Great school district, and if you need to leave your new beautiful and tranquil country living space, you are incredibly close to shopping, freeways, and nightlife--all within 10 minutes.  This is two tax lots and buyer to do own due diligence for additional buildings.  Stop in and see all of the amazing potential in this beautiful property.
